&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://necromuralist.github.io/Terribilis-Ludum/posts/edabit-convert-a-number-to-base-2/index.html#orgb3dc058"&gt;The Tester&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
